events.title: Married to Ashley
events.description: The best day of my life. I married Ashley Alt at the courthouse in downtown Chicago. We had a small ceremony with our family an then went to a nice breakfast at a restaurant in the city. It was a great day.

events.title: I accepted a job offer work at AWS
events.description: After passing my interviews and discussing things with Ashley, I decided to accept the job offer from AWS.

events.title: First day of work at AWS
events.description: I started working for Amazon Web Services as an SDE2 on the "AWS SDK for Rust" team.
